---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Manmeet Kaur">
  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <h2>About Manmeet Kaur</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="profile-grid">
          <div class="profile-section">
            <h2>My Approach to Therapy</h2>
            <p>
              My core belief is that a strong, trusting therapeutic relationship
              is the foundation for change. I am committed to creating a safe,
              empathetic, and non-judgmental space where you feel heard and
              understood. My approach is collaborative and client-centered,
              meaning your unique needs and goals are always at the forefront of
              our work together.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <strong>Comprehensive Initial Assessment:</strong> We begin by exploring
                your history, concerns, and expectations to collaboratively define
                meaningful short-term and long-term goals.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Evidence-Based Interventions:</strong> I utilize proven therapeutic
                techniques to help you understand and work through your thoughts,
                emotions, and behaviors, empowering you with lasting skills.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Holistic and Adaptive Therapy:</strong> I adapt my methods
                to address a wide range of issues, from anxiety and depression to
                trauma and stress, always focusing on your overall well-being.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>In-Depth Assessments:</strong> To gain deeper insight, I
                may use evidence-based tools like personality tests and diagnostic
                measures to inform our therapeutic process effectively.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <aside class="profile-sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-card">
              <h3>Education & Credentials</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Pursuing Ph.D. in Cognitive Neuroscience, IIT Bombay</li>
                <li>Licensed Clinical Psychologist (RCI Registered)</li>
                <li>NET-JRF Qualified</li>
                <li>4 Years of Clinical Experience</li>
                <li>Certified in Basics of Addiction Management</li>
                <li>Certified in Rational Emotive Behavior Therapy (REBT)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-card">
              <h3>Areas of Expertise</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Anxiety and Depression</li>
                <li>Trauma and PTSD</li>
                <li>Relationship Issues</li>
                <li>Stress Management</li>
                <li>Substance Use</li>
                <li>ADHD, Autism</li>
                <li>Anger Management</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    background: #988677;
    padding: 10rem 2rem 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h2 {
    color: white;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .profile-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .profile-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .profile-section p,
  .profile-section ul {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .profile-section li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .sidebar-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sidebar-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .sidebar-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .profile-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .profile-sidebar {
      grid-row: 1; /* Moves sidebar to the top on mobile */
    }
  }
</style>
